DRIVING FORCE:

        On the selection screen, with the mouse pointer click on the two
        'I's in the word {drIvIn} then when you are ready to start hold
        down the 'HELP' key until the game has finished loading. You should
        now see the words "you cheat" appear in the nationality boxes of
        the races, and you will qualify for the next race regardless of the
        position you finish in.  When you start the game, your vehicle will
        not go off of the side of the track, but it can still be hit by
        other cars.
